'''2016年土耳其整肃'''（2016–present purges in Turkey）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/108276379_220012|title=土耳其整肃，149名将领被撤|publisher=搜狐网|date=2016-07-30|accessdate=2019-04-12|archive-date=2019-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412031505/http://www.sohu.com/a/108276379_220012|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160920002864-260408?chdtv|title=土耳其政變後大整肅 2.8萬名教師遭開除|publisher=中時電子報|date=2016-09-20|accessdate=2019-04-12|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912090151/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160920002864-260408?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[2016年土耳其政變|2016年土耳其政變]]失敗後，[[土耳其|土耳其]][[正义与发展党_(土耳其)|正義與發展黨]]政府針對軍方、警察、司法界、各政府部門和機關、教育及學術界、新聞界、宗教團體及其它界別發動的大規模[[肅清|肅清]]。土耳其政府指稱那些被清洗的人與或可能與被指是政變幕後黑手、居於美國的伊斯蘭教士[[法图拉·葛兰|法图拉·葛兰]]有關連。大量土耳其人被當局調查是否與政變有關連。至2016年8月初，已有近7萬人因為被懷疑與「葛蘭運動」有關連，而被當局暫停職務或開除，約18,000人最終被拘留或逮捕。<ref name=dm20160803/>

==清洗行動==
===軍方===
政府在政变失败後开始起诉政变者，初時有2,839名军人遭到逮捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36813924 |title=Turkey: Mass arrests after coup bid quashed, says PM – BBC News |format= |work= |accessdate=16 July 2016 |archive-date=2019-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514220507/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36813924 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/politics/2016/07/16/turkeys-top-judicial-board-hsyk-orders-detention-of-2745-gulen-linked-judges-over-coup-attempt|title=Turkey's top judicial board HSYK orders detention of 2,745 Gülen-linked judges over coup attempt|access-date=2016-07-17|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717151727/http://www.dailysabah.com/politics/2016/07/16/turkeys-top-judicial-board-hsyk-orders-detention-of-2745-gulen-linked-judges-over-coup-attempt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨着拘捕行動擴大，至2016年7月下旬，已有超過9,000名軍人被拘留。<ref name=cn7953896>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-27/7953896.shtml |title=美媒:土耳其未遂政变被捕人士被曝遭虐待 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-07-27 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160802201313/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-27/7953896.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>土耳其官員於7月23日表示已釋放1,200名軍人，全是低軍階的軍人。<ref name=bbc20160724/>

至7月18日，已有103名將領被拘留。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-18/7943362.shtml |title=土耳其解除近9000名官员职务 拘押103名将领 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-07-18 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719140951/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-18/7943362.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

有超過2,500名成員的總統衛隊有近300名成員在政變後被捕。<ref name=bbc20160724>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/07/160724_turkey_coup_presidential_guard |title=土耳其未遂政变：精锐总统卫队被解散 |work=BBC中文網 |date=2016-07-24 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727012349/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2016/07/160724_turkey_coup_presidential_guard |dead-url=no }}</ref>土耳其總理[[比纳利·耶伊尔德勒姆|耶爾德勒姆]]於7月23日表示將會解散總統衛隊。<ref name=cn7949595>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-24/7949595.shtml |title=土耳其宣布解散总统卫队 提前举行最高军委会议 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-07-24 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727083333/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-24/7949595.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===警察和司法界===
近8,000名警察被停職。<ref name=ifeng01>{{Cite news |url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20160718/49380007_0.shtml |title=土耳其軍隊和司法系統6000人被捕30名省長被解職 |work=鳳凰網 |date=2016-07-18 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721102944/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20160718/49380007_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/07/160718_turkey_coup_arrest |title=土耳其未遂政變 ：數千名警察被停職 |work=BBC中文網 |date=2016-07-18 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719184632/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/07/160718_turkey_coup_arrest |dead-url=no }}</ref>

土耳其{{Link-en|法官及檢察官最高委員會|Supreme Board of Judges and Prosecutors}}召開緊急會議，解除數名委員會成員職務，又解除2,745名法官的職務。當局又向近200名行政法院和上訴法院司法人員發出拘捕令，最高行政法院10名成員已被當局扣留。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/turkey-coup-latest-news-erdogan-istanbul-judges-removed-from-duty-failed-government-overthrow-a7140661.html |title=Turkey coup: 2,700 judges removed from duty following failed overthrow attempt |publisher=The Independent |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717104543/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/turkey-coup-latest-news-erdogan-istanbul-judges-removed-from-duty-failed-government-overthrow-a7140661.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&itemid=883611 |title=土耳其拘捕叛變軍人並肅清涉及政變的司法人員 |work=881903.com |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718141054/http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&itemid=883611 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===地方首長===
30名省長被解職。<ref name=ifeng01/>

===教育及學術界===
土耳其教育部於7月19日宣佈開除15,200名員工，理由是他們涉嫌與政變分子有關連。當局又要求全國所有高等教育院校的1,500多名院長全部辭職，實質上等同開除。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2016/07/19/turkeys-education-ministry-reportedly-fires-15200-for-ties-to-failed-coup.html |title=Turkey's education ministry reportedly fires 15,200 for ties to failed coup |work=Fox News |date=2016-07-19 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722173619/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2016/07/19/turkeys-education-ministry-reportedly-fires-15200-for-ties-to-failed-coup.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/en/turkey-fires-all-university-deans-in-post-coup-purge-state-tv/a-19410206 |title=Turkey fires all university deans in post-coup purge - state TV |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-07-19 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722134130/http://www.dw.com/en/turkey-fires-all-university-deans-in-post-coup-purge-state-tv/a-19410206 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同日教育部宣佈吊銷21,000名私營教育機構教師的教師執照，官員表示有情報顯示那些教師大多與恐怖分子活動有關連。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-teachers-idUSKCN0ZZ22F?il=0 |title=Licenses of 21,000 Turkish teachers have been revoked: ministry official |publisher=Reuters |date=2016-07-19 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722140552/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-security-teachers-idUSKCN0ZZ22F?il=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月20日，國營媒體報道當局正在採取行動，關閉626所私營學校和其它教育機構。那些學校被指與[[法图拉·葛兰|法图拉·葛兰]]有關連。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/emergency-meetings-held-as-turkey-reels-from-coup-attempt/3426842.html |title=Erdogan Declares 3-Month State of Emergency |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-07-20 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721120908/http://www.voanews.com/content/emergency-meetings-held-as-turkey-reels-from-coup-attempt/3426842.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>土耳其高等教育委員會禁止學者到國外出差，並要求身處國外的土耳其學者與留學生們儘快返回土耳其。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/en/academics-banned-from-traveling-as-erdogan-convenes-cabinet-security-council/a-19414290 |title=Academics banned from traveling as Erdogan convenes cabinet, security council |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-07-20 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723092746/http://www.dw.com/en/academics-banned-from-traveling-as-erdogan-convenes-cabinet-security-council/a-19414290 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

很多教育單位被深入調查，至2016年7月下旬，最少1,043所私立學校、15所大學已被當局下令關閉。<ref name=cn7949595/>

===新聞界===
至2016年7月27日，土耳其政府已命令45份報章、23間電台、16個電視頻道和3間新聞通訊社停止運作。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/escalation-media-crackdown-turkey-heightens-concerns/3438098.html |title=Escalation of Media Crackdown in Turkey Heightens Concerns |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-07-27 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729143203/http://www.voanews.com/content/escalation-media-crackdown-turkey-heightens-concerns/3438098.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>土耳其最大的報章《[[時代報_(土耳其)|時代報]]》有近50名編輯部前員工被當局發出拘捕令。早些時候，當局向42名新聞工作者發出拘捕令，其中有16人已經被拘押。<ref name=voa3436603>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/turkey-issues-arrest-warrants-for-dozens-more-journalists/3436603.html |title=Turkey Closes Scores of Media Outlets, Dismisses 2,400 Soldiers, Officers |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-07-27 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728144045/http://www.voanews.com/content/turkey-issues-arrest-warrants-for-dozens-more-journalists/3436603.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===其它===
近11,000名被懷疑與政變有關連的土耳其人被政府宣佈吊銷他們的護照。<ref>{{cite news|title=Turkish Authorities Revoke 11,000 Passports in Wake of Failed Coup|url=http://www.sputniknews.com/middleeast/20160722/1043470310/turkey-coup-passports-revoke.html|accessdate=22 July 2016|agency=Sputnik|publisher=Sputnik News|date=22 July 2016|location=Moscow|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160726135851/http://sputniknews.com/middleeast/20160722/1043470310/turkey-coup-passports-revoke.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[土耳其航空公司|土耳其航空公司]]於7月25日宣佈開除211人。<ref name=cn7953896/>

至2016年7月下旬，最少1,229個慈善組織和基金會、19個工會和35家醫療機構已被當局下令關閉。<ref name=cn7949595/>

2016年8月初的報道指[[土耳其足球總會|土耳其足球總會]]已開除105名足球裁判等人員。<ref name=dm20160803>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3720652/Turkish-board-fires-105-staff-following-coup-attempt.html |title=Turkey sacks 105 referees as Erdogan continues his crackdown for failed coup |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-08-03 |accessdate=2016-08-08 |archive-date=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804195648/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3720652/Turkish-board-fires-105-staff-following-coup-attempt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年10月18日，土耳其[[慈善家|慈善家]][[奥斯曼·卡瓦拉|奥斯曼·卡瓦拉]]在[[伊斯坦堡阿塔圖克機場|伊斯坦堡阿塔圖克機場]]被捕<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2018/11/turkey-mysterious-one-year-imprisonment-of-osman-kavala.html|title=Still no charges for Turkey's top philanthropist after year behind bars|last=Gursel|first=Kadri|date=2018-11-05|work=Al-Monitor|access-date=2018-11-08|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128035042/https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2018/11/turkey-mysterious-one-year-imprisonment-of-osman-kavala.html}}</ref>；10月25日，土耳其亲埃尔多安的媒体《{{Translink|en|Daily Sabah|每日晨报}}》指控他是“背景可疑的商业大亨”、“与[[居伦运动|居伦运动]]有联系”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/investigations/2017/10/25/detained-tycoon-osman-kavala-linked-to-feto-coup-attempts|title=Detained tycoon Osman Kavala linked to FETÖ coup attempts|publisher={{Translink|en|Daily Sabah|每日晨报}}|date=2017-10-25|accessdate=2021-10-24|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122124855/https://www.dailysabah.com/investigations/2017/10/25/detained-tycoon-osman-kavala-linked-to-feto-coup-attempts}}</ref>。

==侵犯人權的指控==
2016年7月下旬，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]表示許多被扣留人士遭到不人道的待遇，包括被虐打和沒有足夠的水和食物，有高級軍官被警察用警棍和手指進行[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]。土耳其司法部長否認指控。<ref name=cn7953896/>

==反應與評論==
一些觀察家把2016年土耳其軍事政變與1933年德國[[国会纵火案|国会纵火案]]相提並論，認為兩者都被當權者利用作為清除政治上反對者的藉口。雖然埃爾多安宣稱政府採取的行動鞏固了民主，{{Link-en|拉爾夫·彼得斯|Ralph Peters}}認為埃爾多安版的民主還不如[[弗拉基米尔·弗拉基米罗维奇·普京|普京]]，埃爾多安從總統走向“[[苏丹_(称谓)|苏丹]]”兼“[[哈里发|哈里发]]”之路只是時間問題。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/opinion/2016/07/21/turkey-and-erdogan-here-comes-real-caliphate.html |title=Turkey and Erdogan: Here comes the (real) caliphate |work=Fox News |date=2016-07-21 |author=Ralph Peters |quote=Various observers have likened the coup’s effect to that of the Reichstag Fire, the murky arson at the German parliament that provided Hitler with the excuse to stamp out all political opposition. ... |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160724022032/http://www.foxnews.com/opinion/2016/07/21/turkey-and-erdogan-here-comes-real-caliphate.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]於2016年7月下旬表示，土耳其當局對新聞媒體採取的一些行動代表着一種「令人不安的勢頭」。<ref name=voa3436603/>

2021年10月，美国、德国、加拿大、丹麦、芬兰、法国、荷兰、新西兰、挪威和瑞典10国的驻土耳其大使一齐向土耳其政府施压，要求释放[[奥斯曼·卡瓦拉|奥斯曼·卡瓦拉]]，随后埃尔多安宣布将上述10国大使列为“[[不受歡迎人物|不受歡迎人物]]”<ref>{{Cite news|last=Pitel|first=Laura|date=2021-10-23|title=Erdogan declares 10 western ambassadors persona non grata|work=[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]|url=https://www.ft.com/content/5d0cec70-3c7e-46e7-a3cf-4330e72328ca|access-date=2021-10-23|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218021621/https://www.ft.com/content/5d0cec70-3c7e-46e7-a3cf-4330e72328ca}}</ref>。

